premise_source_doc_sentence: Following the Jawaharlal Nehru Technological Universities Act , 2008 Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University was split into four universities , Jawaharlal Nehru Architecture and Fine Arts University , Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University , Anantapur , Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University , Hyderabad and Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University , Kakinada .
